scriptmanager.scripts.Figure_Generation

Class ThreeColorHeatMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • scriptmanager.scripts.Figure_Generation.ThreeColorHeatMap

  • public class ThreeColorHeatMap
extends java.lang.Object
    The script to generate a three-color heamap PNG (with a an adjustable middling value for the middle color) from a matrix of values in tab-delmited/CDT format.
    Author:
    Olivia Lang
    See Also:
    ThreeColorHeatMapCLI, ThreeColorHeatMapOutput, ThreeColorHeatMapWindow
